{"id":916882309,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 months, 1 week","timestamp":1679060528,"status":11,"status_display":"Wrong Answer","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/916882309/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Minimum Time to Complete All Tasks","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\n    public int findMinimumTime(int[][] tasks) {\n        Arrays.sort(tasks,(a,b)-> a[1]==b[1] ? a[0]-b[0] : a[1]-b[1]);\n        HashSet<Integer> hs=new HashSet<>();\n        for(int[] i: tasks){\n            int used=0;\n            for(int j=i[0];j<=i[1];j++){\n                if(hs.contains(j)){\n                    used++;\n                }\n            }\n            int rem=i[2]-used;\n            int end=i[1];\n            for(int j=rem;j>0;j--){\n                hs.add(end);\n                end--;\n            }\n        }\n        return hs.size();\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"minimum-time-to-complete-all-tasks","has_notes":false}
